      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for Mesa fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2023-45913: Fixed NULL pointer dereference via dri2GetGlxDrawableFromXDrawableId() (bsc#1222040)\n- CVE-2023-45919: Fixed buffer over-read in glXQueryServerString() (bsc#1222041)\n- CVE-2023-45922: Fixed segmentation violation in __glXGetDrawableAttribute() (bsc#1222042)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
